// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0562 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 019774ee-2995-5af4-a682-d895195ce650

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:5*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:6*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*")
